GRAY, Respondent, v. CRONER et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Henry Winthrop Gray, as receiver, etc., against Benjamin ■Craner and another.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

I. L. Bamberger and Grants Nathan, for appellants. Burrill, Zabriskie & Burrill, for respondent.

No opinion. Order denying motion to increase undertaking on injunction affirmed, with costs.
